Package kimononet.geo

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    GeoDevice
    Interface that represents a GPS enabled device.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultGeoDevice
    GPS enabled device that emulates a stationary device.
    GeoLocation
    Object stores location in terms of longitude, latitude, and accuracy as well as keeps track of last update time.
    GeoMap
    Represents a map bounded by upper left and bottom right corners.
    GeoService  
    GeoVelocity
    The class represents a GPS velocity vector in terms of speed and a bearing.
    RandomWaypointGeoDevice
    GPS enabled device emulator that provided an initial location and velocity, acts according to the the Random Waypoint Model .

    GeoLocationException  
    GeoMapException
